flowchart TD
    A[RoundManager admits eligible container index] --> B{Which waiting list?}
    B -- Ingress --> C[TIngressWaitingList]
    B -- Dispatch --> D[TDispatchWaitingList]

    C --> E[ReferencePrecalculator consumes ingress indices]
    D --> F[ReferencePrecalculator consumes dispatch indices]

    E --> G[Resolve TContainer via TContainerRegistry]
    F --> H[Resolve TContainer via TContainerRegistry]

    G --> I[Check container state + slot state + round context]
    H --> J[Check container state + slot state + round context]

    I --> K[Prepare TIngressAccessRef]
    J --> L[Prepare TDispatchAccessRef]

    K --> M[Ingress consumes next ref]
    L --> N[Dispatcher consumes next ref]

    M --> O[Envelope placed into slot]
    N --> P[Dispatch exposure to bridge-facing side]
